Package com.ausregistry.jtoolkit2.session Description

Provides the interfaces and classes necessary to interact with an EPP server. The factories SessionFactory and SessionManagerFactory provide implementations of the Session and SessionManager interfaces respectively. Instructions for how to change the implementation provided by the factory are provided in the documentation for those classes.
